Package: digiRhythm
Type: Package
Title: digiRhythm for analyzing and visualizing animal's Rhythmicity.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: Roland-Hassan Nasser <roland.nasser@agroscope.admin.c>
Description: digiRhythm is an R library developed at Agroscope and provides a set of tools to 
analyze and visualize the rhythmic behavior of animals.
    The main functionalities of this library are: computing the degree of functional
coupling, visualizing actograms, clustering day-animal activities and more.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
